<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vritdp0QSwU/WG91rOM6EJI/AAAAAAAALZo/Nwop1nHUoacnVv1uxbKL-yqnbfUW_9OyQCLcB/s1600/AP1050063.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="438" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vritdp0QSwU/WG91rOM6EJI/AAAAAAAALZo/Nwop1nHUoacnVv1uxbKL-yqnbfUW_9OyQCLcB/s640/AP1050063.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eLssHD9Fya4/WG91tm1N-XI/AAAAAAAALZs/-cqUbWV5Gj80iAfzxNTIfARPT5X3OOrPQCLcB/s1600/AP1050036.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="414" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eLssHD9Fya4/WG91tm1N-XI/AAAAAAAALZs/-cqUbWV5Gj80iAfzxNTIfARPT5X3OOrPQCLcB/s640/AP1050036.jpg" width="640" /></a></div>Another gloriously bright day today. The snow that was laying over the highest hills has now largely gone but what was left of it, all well as the ground, had frozen hard. Cold enough in fact for a touch of improvised ice skating. Jo and myself tripped round a circuit of <i>Aran Fawddwy (905m)</i> from Cwm Cywarch enjoying the fine weather and the wide views of the whole of Snowdonia and beyond.&nbsp; <br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-42HP0rR9hPE/WG91vpWGIcI/AAAAAAAALZw/I3TMPfTa8OsJyvDeymgSBHXGhN2Y4BmowCLcB/s1600/AP1050051.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="416" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-42HP0rR9hPE/WG91vpWGIcI/AAAAAAAALZw/I3TMPfTa8OsJyvDeymgSBHXGhN2Y4BmowCLcB/s640/AP1050051.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QLbJ72Lx5yg/WG91zn8w9QI/AAAAAAAALZ0/nvT_VXr4jXgs95LRU3Qd5VZquhZMXmvEgCLcB/s1600/AP1050068.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="418" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QLbJ72Lx5yg/WG91zn8w9QI/AAAAAAAALZ0/nvT_VXr4jXgs95LRU3Qd5VZquhZMXmvEgCLcB/s640/AP1050068.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/--98UXZLfdjc/WG910u57owI/AAAAAAAALZ4/386bjMbqnDgkkHh1Jg6mz7Sm-8K1Q470wCLcB/s1600/AP1050071.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="400" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/--98UXZLfdjc/WG910u57owI/AAAAAAAALZ4/386bjMbqnDgkkHh1Jg6mz7Sm-8K1Q470wCLcB/s640/AP1050071.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Mub_X6Ug5qQ/WG911IwqLxI/AAAAAAAALZ8/pd-ij29xoeww8neR_79xJBMhUPcghC0wQCLcB/s1600/AIMG_7809.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="398" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Mub_X6Ug5qQ/WG911IwqLxI/AAAAAAAALZ8/pd-ij29xoeww8neR_79xJBMhUPcghC0wQCLcB/s640/AIMG_7809.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VzhxJXMhPLQ/WG913dhtsHI/AAAAAAAALaA/PGaVxJ3pTD46gStXrZXU72JKhOwEbp-HwCLcB/s1600/AP1050088.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="414" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VzhxJXMhPLQ/WG913dhtsHI/AAAAAAAALaA/PGaVxJ3pTD46gStXrZXU72JKhOwEbp-HwCLcB/s640/AP1050088.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br />